hindi mahalaga,

00:34:19.320 --> 00:34:20.280
at wala itong kinalaman

00:34:20.280 --> 00:34:22.420
sa pagiging co-author ko

00:34:22.920 --> 00:34:23.580
sa libro.

00:34:24.070 --> 00:34:26.100
Mentor, ako...

00:34:26.920 --> 00:34:28.030
Bumangon ka muna.

00:34:32.400 --> 00:34:34.710
Hindi mo kailangang magmadali upang magdesisyon ng anuman.

00:34:34.710 --> 00:34:36.570
Pagkatapos ng lahat, ang Coroners' Contest

00:34:36.750 --> 00:34:39.679
hindi isasara ang pagpaparehistro
para sa isa pang tatlong araw.

00:34:39.840 --> 00:34:42.960
Ngunit may isang bagay
na kailangang hawakan ngayon.

00:34:42.960 --> 00:34:44.280
naisulat ko na

00:34:44.360 --> 00:34:47.290
ang abiso na nagpapaalis kay Zhong Shizai
sa aking pag-aalaga.

00:34:47.480 --> 00:34:48.760
Ang dahilan kung bakit ko ito ginagawa

00:34:48.760 --> 00:34:49.690
ay upang maiwasan

00:34:49.800 --> 00:34:50.880
ang malapit nang mai-publish

00:34:50.880 --> 00:34:53.139
manwal ng mga coroner mula sa kahihiyan.

00:34:53.550 --> 00:34:54.840
Naiintindihan mo ba?

00:34:55.670 --> 00:34:56.469
naiintindihan ko.

00:34:56.880 --> 00:34:58.110
Si Zhong Shizai ay naiinip
sa kanyang paghahangad ng tagumpay

00:34:58.110 --> 00:34:58.970
at dalawang mukha.

00:34:59.110 --> 00:35:01.240
Dapat matagal mo na siyang pinaalis.

00:35:03.000 --> 00:35:05.070
Ngunit ayon sa mga patakaran
ng aming propesyon,

00:35:05.070 --> 00:35:05.880
paunawa na ito

00:35:05.920 --> 00:35:08.320
kailangang pirmahan ninyong dalawa,
mga alagad ko.

00:35:08.550 --> 00:35:10.880
Yao, hindi ka marunong bumasa o sumulat
noong bata ka,

00:35:11.070 --> 00:35:12.380
pero narinig ko

00:35:12.480 --> 00:35:14.110
na natutunan mo ngayon.

00:35:14.590 --> 00:35:15.190
Oo.

00:35:16.000 --> 00:35:17.760
Sa tatlong taon
mula nang umalis sa propesyon ng coroner,

00:35:17.760 --> 00:35:19.550
bukod sa pagtatrabaho bilang isang mortician,

00:35:19.550 --> 00:35:20.640
Nag-aral ako

00:35:20.670 --> 00:35:22.330
at nagsasanay ng kaligrapya.

00:35:24.960 --> 00:35:26.760
Napakasipag mo, Yao.

00:35:27.320 --> 00:35:28.710
Sana balang araw,

00:35:29.440 --> 00:35:31.440
kapag minana ko ang iyong pamana, Mentor,

00:35:31.590 --> 00:35:33.450
hindi sasabihin ng mga tao na hindi ako marunong magbasa.

00:35:34.630 --> 00:35:35.110
Mabuti.

00:35:36.840 --> 00:35:37.840
Sumama ka sa akin.

00:35:41.710 --> 00:35:44.220
[Paunawa ng Pagpatalsik para kay Zhong Shizai]

00:35:44.220 --> 00:35:45.190
[Saksi: Suchan]

00:35:45.190 --> 00:35:45.800
Tingnan mo.

00:35:46.520 --> 00:35:46.590
[Mentor: Geng Wushang]

00:35:46.590 --> 00:35:47.960
pinirmahan ko na,

00:35:48.360 --> 00:35:49.950
at pumirma na rin si Suchan.

00:35:50.880 --> 00:35:52.010
Ngayon kailangan ka lang namin.

00:36:09.040 --> 00:36:11.430
[Mga Saksi: Suchan; Yin Yao]

00:36:12.030 --> 00:36:13.160
Isulat ang petsa.

00:36:15.030 --> 00:36:16.400
ika-23 ng Hunyo.

00:36:35.110 --> 00:36:35.710
Mentor,

00:36:36.890 --> 00:36:37.840
ayos ka lang ba

00:36:42.920 --> 00:36:43.710
ayos lang ako.

00:36:46.510 --> 00:36:47.370
alam ko.

00:36:48.360 --> 00:36:50.490
Pagkatapos ng lahat, sinundan ka ni Senior Shizai
sa loob ng maraming taon.

00:36:50.490 --> 00:36:52.150
Ngunit Guro, hindi mo kailangang malungkot.

00:36:52.150 --> 00:36:53.440
Hindi naman sa wala kang puso.

00:36:53.440 --> 00:36:54.630
Si Zhong Shizai mismo—

00:36:54.630 --> 00:36:56.290
dinala niya ito sa kanyang sarili.

00:36:56.550 --> 00:36:57.630
Nakapagdesisyon na ako

00:36:57.630 --> 00:36:59.690
kung ano ang isusulat para sa huling kabanata.

00:37:00.360 --> 00:37:01.290
Magsusulat ako tungkol sa

00:37:01.990 --> 00:37:04.530
bakit hindi dapat pumatay ang isang coroner.

00:37:06.480 --> 00:37:07.190
Guro,

00:37:07.710 --> 00:37:09.030
patawarin mo ang aking katapatan,

00:37:09.880 --> 00:37:11.610
pero hindi ba obvious?

00:37:11.840 --> 00:37:13.540
Walang pwedeng pumatay.

00:37:13.930 --> 00:37:15.060
Mangyaring muling isaalang-alang.

00:37:15.230 --> 00:37:16.810
Dapat may mas magandang paksa

00:37:16.960 --> 00:37:18.840
para tapusin ang "The Autopsy Chronicles."

00:37:18.840 --> 00:37:20.440
Ngunit ang aking kalusugan ...

00:37:20.550 --> 00:37:21.340
Huwag kang mag-alala.

00:37:21.710 --> 00:37:23.800
Marami ka pang taon sa unahan mo.

00:37:23.800 --> 00:37:24.960
Paano mo malalaman?

00:37:28.760 --> 00:37:30.160
Kahit na lumipat na ako,

00:37:30.670 --> 00:37:31.760
hindi ba kita dinadalaw

00:37:31.780 --> 00:37:32.840
tuwing tatlong araw?

00:37:33.320 --> 00:37:35.770
Sa totoo lang, tuwing tatlong araw,

00:37:36.480 --> 00:37:37.510
Pumunta din ako sa templo

00:37:37.510 --> 00:37:38.840
upang manalangin para sa iyong mahabang buhay.

00:37:38.840 --> 00:37:40.880
Ako ay pinagkalooban
ng banal na paghahayag matagal na ang nakalipas,

00:37:40.880 --> 00:37:42.480
hinuhulaan na marami ka pang
taon upang mabuhay.

00:37:42.480 --> 00:37:44.140
Senior Yin, napakabait mo.

00:37:44.280 --> 00:37:45.880
Ako, si Suchan, hindi nasusukat.

00:38:12.320 --> 00:38:13.010
Su Wuming!

00:38:13.280 --> 00:38:14.480
May isa pang pagpatay!

00:38:14.480 --> 00:38:15.310
Isang pulubi

00:38:15.510 --> 00:38:17.710
nakapulot din ng supot na panghihiram ng buhay!

00:38:19.400 --> 00:38:21.180
Ipatawag si Coroner Suchan.

00:38:22.030 --> 00:38:24.500
Dumating si Coroner Suchan upang
suriin ang katawan!

00:38:24.960 --> 00:38:26.420
Lahat ng walang kaugnayang tauhan,

00:38:26.510 --> 00:38:27.110
umatras!

00:38:45.560 --> 00:38:49.040
[Anim]

00:39:29.960 --> 00:39:31.400
Ama, bumalik na ako.

00:39:35.280 --> 00:39:35.950
Ama!

00:39:38.760 --> 00:39:39.550
Ama!

00:39:41.840 --> 00:39:42.670
Su Wuming!

00:39:43.360 --> 00:39:45.580
Diba sabi mo gusto mong kumain ng sushan?

00:39:45.960 --> 00:39:47.360
May dala ako para sayo!

00:39:47.440 --> 00:39:49.900
Bilis, samahan mo ako
sa bahay ni Coroner Geng.

00:39:55.680 --> 00:40:00.100
[Gang]

00:40:02.090 --> 00:40:05.570
[Gang Residence]

